The paper proposes a new actor-critic algorithm for reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also discusses the application of the proposed algorithm to safe RL, domain knowledge, and transfer learning, which are all subfields of RL. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
